{"section": "Exercise 2.12.1: Computing a multiplicative inverse.", "qid": 1, "instructions": "<div class=\"activity-instructions\">\n</div>\n", "question": "<div class=\"question\">\n <div class=\"setup flex-row\">\n  <div class=\"label\">\n   2)\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   Euclid's algorithm returns\n   <br/>\n   gcd(14, 33) = 1 = 3 \u00b7 33 - 7 \u00b7 14.\n   <br/>\n   <br/>\n   What is the multiplicative inverse of 14 in\n   <b>\n    Z\n   </b>\n   <sub>\n    33\n   </sub>\n   ?\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"question-container flex-row\">\n  <div class=\"input\">\n   <pre><!----><textarea class=\"zb-text-area hide-scrollbar ember-text-area ember-view\" cols=\"20\" id=\"ember106\" rows=\"1\" spellcheck=\"false\"></textarea><!----></pre>\n   <div class=\"buttons flex-row\">\n    <button class=\"check-button zb-button primary raised ember-view\" id=\"ember107\">\n     <!-- -->\n     <span class=\"title\">\n      Check\n     </span>\n    </button>\n    <button class=\"show-answer-button zb-button secondary ember-view\" id=\"ember108\" style=\"\">\n     <!-- -->\n     <span class=\"title\">\n      Show answer\n     </span>\n    </button>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n</div>\n", "choices": [], "answer": "<div class=\"answer\">\n <p>\n  From the solution to the previous problem:\n </p>\n <p>\n  gcd(77, 52) = 1 = 25\u00b777 - 37\u00b752\n </p>\n <p>\n  The coefficient of 77 in the equation above is 25. The multiplicative inverse of 77 mod 52\nis (25 mod 52) = 25.\n </p>\n <p>\n  Check: 77\u00b725 mod 52 = 1925 mod 52 = 1\n </p>\n</div>\n", "explanation": null}